Zapatero Backs Rubalcaba as Socialist Candidate , Efe Says

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-05-27T18:36:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-27/zapatero-backs-rubalcaba-as-socialist-candidate-efe-says.html
Spanish Prime Minister Jose Luis
Rodriguez Zapatero backed Deputy Prime Minister Alfredo Perez
Rubalcaba as the Socialist party’s candidate for general
elections due in March 2012, Efe newswire reported.  The party may still commence the process of primary
elections at a meeting tomorrow, the newswire said, citing
people in the party it didn’t identify.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  